  <brief_title>Evaluation of the AO Pediatric Classification for Long Bones Fractures Like a Guide for Treatment and Prognosis</brief_title>
  <acronym>AO-PC</acronym>
  <official_title>Phase 2/3 Eficacy Study of the AO Pediatric Classification in Treatment and Prognosis of Long Bones Fractures</official_title>
